OL,3,CRoyal Mail CEO: 6,500 postal workers
OL,4,Coff sick every day
OL,6,FThe CEO of Royal Mail has warned that
OL,7,Fthousands of postal workers are off
OL,8,Fsick every day, costing the
OL,9,Forganisation around #200 million a
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FSpeaking at The Times CEO summit on
OL,13,FThursday, Martin Seidenberg, the head
OL,14,Fof International Distribution Services
OL,15,F(IDS), Royal Mail's owner, said that
OL,16,Faround 6,500 postal workers out of a
OL,17,Ftotal of about 130,000 employees are
OL,18,Foff sick everyday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
