FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781880484
OL,3,CRoyal Mail CEO: 6,500 postal workers
OL,4,Coff sick every day
OL,6,F"It has a cost to us, and of course an
OL,7,Fimpact to you, to society, because of
OL,8,Fthe quality that we can deliver or not
OL,9,Fdeliver," Seidenberg said, adding that
OL,10,Fthis was "super important for us to
OL,11,Ffix".
OL,13,FIn response to its issues with
OL,14,Fsickness absence, the IDS has given
OL,15,Fall of its staff 24-hour access to an
OL,16,Fonline GP, he said.
OL,18,F"We've been very surprised how heavily
OL,19,Fthis is being used," Seidenberg sai.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]rD@JOUsD@DO]zD@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
