OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781880484
OL,3,CRoyal Mail CEO: 6,500 postal workers
OL,4,Coff sick every day
OL,6,F"We like it, because quite frankly, we
OL,7,Fbelieve that the sooner we can take
OL,8,Fcare of our people and they have
OL,9,Faccess to medical support, the sooner
OL,10,Fthey're likely to return to the job."
OL,12,FLast month it was revealed Royal Mail
OL,13,Fhad missed its delivery target for
OL,14,Fanother year running, in the 12 months
OL,15,Fto March. It comes after after the
OL,16,Fpostal service pledged to invest #500
OL,17,Fmillion in improving its service.
