OL,3,CRoyal Mail CEO: 6,500 postal workers
OL,4,Coff sick every day
OL,6,FRoyal Mail said it had been a
OL,7,Fchallenging start to the year, and
OL,8,Fthat storms Goretti and Chandra, as
OL,9,Fwell as more staff calling in sick
OL,10,Ffrom the flu, had affected its
OL,11,Fperformance over the winter.
