OL,3,CRoyal Mail CEO: 6,500 postal workers
OL,4,Coff sick every day
OL,6,FAround 75.7% of first-class mail
OL,7,Farrived the next working day,
OL,8,Faccording to the latest quality of
OL,9,Fservice report, which was slightly
OL,10,Fless than the 76.3% achieved in the
OL,11,Fprior year.
OL,13,FFor second-class mail, 90.2% was
OL,14,Fdelivered within three working days `
OL,15,Fless than the 92.2% achieved the year
OL,16,Fbefore.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
