OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781880484
OL,3,CRoyal Mail CEO: 6,500 postal workers
OL,4,Coff sick every day
OL,6,FUnder the watchdog's targets, 90% of
OL,7,Ffirst-class mail should be delivered
OL,8,Fthe next day, and 95% of second-class
OL,9,Fmail should be delivered within three
OL,10,Fdays.
OL,12,FRoyal Mail was fined #21 million by
OL,13,FOfcom in October last year for missing
OL,14,Fits annual targets ` the third-largest
OL,15,Ffine ever imposed by the
OL,16,Fcommunications watchdog.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
